<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>예측 · k-ant-daily</title>
<style>
{% include '_theme.css.j2' %}
  body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--fg);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;
  }
  main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 20px 64px; }
  h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  .hint { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  li { padding: 12px 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; }
  li { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  li > a.primary { color: var(--fg); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  li > a.primary:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  li .date { font-weight: 600; }
  li .tldr { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  li .retro {
    color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 8px; border: 1px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 999px;
    white-space: nowrap; opacity: 0.9;
  }
  li .retro:hover { opacity: 1; background: var(--card); }
  nav { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  nav a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <nav><a href="index.html">← 오늘자</a> · <a href="game.html">🎲 맞춰봐</a></nav>
  <h1>📋 예측</h1>
  <p class="hint">일별 장전 브리핑 {{ entries|length }}개 · 각 날짜의 아침 예측 아카이브</p>
  <ul>
    {% for e in entries %}
    <li>
      <a class="primary" href="{{ e.filename }}">
        <span class="date">{{ e.date }}</span>
        <span class="tldr">{{ e.tldr }}</span>
      </a>
      {% if e.has_retro %}
      <a class="retro" href="accuracy/{{ e.date }}.html" title="그날의 예측 vs 결과 회고">🔍 회고</a>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</main>
</body>
</html>
